<a href="/questions/900811-what-is-this-guys-point-that-it-is-best">What is this guys point? That it is best not to have war? Well, thank you for that insightful opinion. I think we all agree on that point. Just like mot sane people know that you aren&#39;t going to have Democracy, freedom, or prosperity without putting boots on foreign soil when you need to do it. ISIS is kind of a good example. They are certainly not at all horrified by violence, which kind of makes Trumbo&#39;s point moot</a>
</div>
