    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1513346466" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13017358228299041026">What a kick in the guts! As many have already pointed out, this should be a required reading for all those who sit in their nice sunny offices and send other people&apos;s kids to war... <br/>I&apos;ve discovered Trumbo very late, but fortunately not too late.</span>
  <span id="freeText13017358228299041026" style="display:none">What a kick in the guts! As many have already pointed out, this should be a required reading for all those who sit in their nice sunny offices and send other people's kids to war... <br />I've discovered Trumbo very late, but fortunately not too late.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13017358228299041026" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
