<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/8497491-lost-and-found-in-russia"><img alt="Lost and Found in Russia: Lives in the Post-Soviet Landscape" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1320484611l/8497491._SX98_.jpg" />
